OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOvernight low cloud burning
OL,6,Fback to the coast this morning,
OL,7,Flingering in a few places into the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Otherwise dry and sunny.
OL,9,FWarm inland but cooler along the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will remain dry with some
OL,14,Flow cloud and fog patches.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FLow cloud burning back to
OL,17,Fthe coast in the morning where it may
OL,18,Flinger into the afternoon. Otherwise
OL,19,Fanother dry and sunny day. Very warm
OL,20,Finland, cooler in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
