OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying dry with some sunshine, still
OL,7,Fsome low cloud along the east coast.
OL,8,FWarm, locally hot on Thursday in the
OL,9,Fwest. Eastern coastal areas cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
